    <title>Other products</title>
    <para>A range of products can be sold through onCourse. You have already seen how you can create
        classes and open them for enrolment at any price you set. In addition to enrolments in
        classes you can also sell:</para>
    <para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>Memberships</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Vouchers</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Products</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </para>
    <para>In this chapter we'll focus on the last of these items: product sales.</para>
